description:
Corey is 23 and built!

He works out 5-6 times a week and is working to put on ever more muscle.

Other than living at the gym, Corey said he likes to watch movies, hang out, and play sports.

He's straight and says he has "several" girlfriends.

"I'm not committed to any single one, " he said. "I'm just kind of playing the field."

Check out the squirts when he comes... powerful!
title: Corey
